PURPOSE

  This module offers basic control of ANSI compliant terminals.


AUTHOR

   Christophe.Troestler@umons.ac.be


LIMITATIONS

  It was hoped that it works on window$ but, in order to have an ANSI
  terminal, you have to run DOS only programs which OCaml programs are
  not.  If anyone knows how to run it on windows, please write to me.


COMPILE & INSTALL

  See the file INSTALL.


